snippet.title: Mr. Triangle Mania 2 - """Release""" Trailer (that's 2 years late)
snippet.description:
https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/mr-triangle-mania-2.760/

Yeah, I was too busy not doing things after months of doing things to do things. Like making the trailer and informing people that the thing I did is out. But here it is, along with a somewhat big update.
And yeah I did just rehash the demo trailer with the sonic music that isn't even in the game :D
